{"version":1,"name":"모르는 길","blueprints":[{"id":1,"title":"굽이 1","objectLabel":"","emoji":"·","position":[-0.29,0,-0.0],"scale":1,"hue":"#eee5d3","objectKit":"none","pathKind":"meadow","surface":"moss-aged","weather":"clear","cameraShot":"side","importance":1,"stillness":0.35,"soundTone":174,"text":"모르는 길을\n걷는 동안은\n어디에도\n늦지 않는다."},{"id":2,"title":"굽이 2","objectLabel":"","emoji":"·","position":[-0.95,0,-2.8],"scale":1,"hue":"#eee5d3","objectKit":"none","pathKind":"meadow","surface":"moss-aged","weather":"clear","cameraShot":"side","importance":1,"stillness":0.35,"soundTone":174,"text":"이 굽이 너머를\n모른다는 게\n오늘의\n다행이다."},{"id":3,"title":"굽이 3","objectLabel":"","emoji":"·","position":[-1.27,0,-5.6],"scale":1,"hue":"#eee5d3","objectKit":"none","pathKind":"meadow","surface":"moss-aged","weather":"clear","cameraShot":"side","importance":1,"stillness":0.35,"soundTone":174,"text":"안개가\n지도를\n지워주었다."},{"id":4,"title":"굽이 4","objectLabel":"","emoji":"·","position":[-1.54,0,-8.4],"scale":1,"hue":"#eee5d3","objectKit":"none","pathKind":"meadow","surface":"moss-aged","weather":"clear","cameraShot":"side","importance":1,"stillness":0.35,"soundTone":174,"text":"돌아가는 길인지\n떠나는 길인지\n묻지 않기로 했다."},{"id":5,"title":"굽이 5","objectLabel":"","emoji":"·","position":[-1.09,0,-11.2],"scale":1,"hue":"#eee5d3","objectKit":"none","pathKind":"meadow","surface":"moss-aged","weather":"clear","cameraShot":"side","importance":1,"stillness":0.35,"soundTone":174,"text":"언덕 하나를\n넘을 때마다\n마음이 한 뼘\n가벼워진다."},{"id":6,"title":"굽이 6","objectLabel":"","emoji":"·","position":[-0.2,0,-14.0],"scale":1,"hue":"#eee5d3","objectKit":"none","pathKind":"meadow","surface":"moss-aged","weather":"clear","cameraShot":"side","importance":1,"stillness":0.35,"soundTone":174,"text":"낯선 굽이에서\n낯익은 바람이\n분다."},{"id":7,"title":"굽이 7","objectLabel":"","emoji":"·","position":[0.9,0,-16.8],"scale":1,"hue":"#eee5d3","objectKit":"none","pathKind":"meadow","surface":"moss-aged","weather":"clear","cameraShot":"side","importance":1,"stillness":0.